Schrodinger equation?

00:02:58.090 --> 00:03:03.890
I need e to the
minus i Et over h.

00:03:03.890 --> 00:03:05.350
And I need it here as well.

00:03:10.470 --> 00:03:16.340
And this is a psi
now of x and t.

00:03:16.340 --> 00:03:19.490
There's two options for x,
less than 0 and x less than 0,

00:03:19.490 --> 00:03:20.710
