00:04:30.900 --> 00:04:34.360
Now superposition.

00:04:34.360 --> 00:04:36.050
That will still
be a solution if I

00:04:36.050 --> 00:04:43.978
do the same superposition in
the two formulas, integral dk

00:04:43.978 --> 00:04:47.150
and integral dk.

00:04:47.150 --> 00:04:50.960
That's still a solution
