00:05:13.580 --> 00:05:14.840
It's not so good.

00:05:14.840 --> 00:05:18.410
Why is not so good, minus
infinity to infinity?

00:05:23.020 --> 00:05:26.310
Would I have to do from
minus infinity on my force.

