Does anybody force me?

00:05:27.801 --> 00:05:28.300
No.

00:05:28.300 --> 00:05:30.430
You're superimposing solutions.

00:05:30.430 --> 00:05:34.030
For different values of
k, you're superimposing.

00:05:34.030 --> 00:05:36.520
You had a solution,
and another solution

00:05:36.520 --> 00:05:37.930
for another, another solution.

00:05:40.520 --> 00:05:45.125
What goes wrong if I go from
